---
import ServiceLayout from '../../components/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Equine-Assisted Occupational Therapy"
  description="Develop your skills and achieve your goals with horses. Equine-assisted occupational therapy in Pakenham, facilitated by OTs with extensive equestrian experience."
  image="/images/services/equine-therapy.jpg"
>
  <img src="/images/services/equine-therapy.jpg" alt="Equine-assisted therapy session at Adventure Therapy Services" class="hero-image" />

  <h2>What to Expect</h2>
  <p>Here's what to expect when getting started with equine-assisted therapy.</p>
  <p>Please check our <a href="/faqs/">frequently asked questions</a> page for information on our fees & charges and anything you're unsure of.</p>
  <p>Parent coaching sessions are run in conjunction with Equine Assisted Therapy. See <a href="/services/parent-coaching/">Parent Coaching</a> for more information.</p>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Initial Assessment via Telehealth</h3>
        <p>The purpose of this session is to gather as much information about you as possible.</p>
        <p>Let's get to know each other and identify what you need and how we can help.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Face to Face at home or school</h3>
        <p>The purpose of these sessions are to develop goals and determine your suitability for the outdoor clinic.</p>
        <p>When we introduce animals to a therapy session it increases the risk, therefore it is important that we ensure everyone's safety.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Outdoor clinic induction</h3>
        <p>The first session at our beautiful outdoor clinic is an opportunity to explore the area and go through what we do to stay safe and have fun!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">4</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Individual program development</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Identify your therapy goals</li>
          <li>Identify therapy services to be included (eg. combination of equine-assisted therapy and parent coaching)</li>
          <li>Identify the frequency of services</li>
          <li>Schedule assessments and outcome measures</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="image-gallery">
    <img src="/images/services/equine-outdoor.jpg" alt="Outdoor equine therapy at 309 Army Road Pakenham" loading="lazy" />
    <img src="/images/services/equine-closeup.jpg" alt="Child interacting with therapy horse" loading="lazy" />
    <img src="/images/services/equine-group.jpg" alt="Group equine-assisted therapy session" loading="lazy" />
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
